ing courses) 2. AI Content Creation Engine (replaces templates/packs) 3. AI Automation Architect (replaces manual setup courses) This is more valuable because it's DONE-FOR-YOU vs. her TEACH-HOW model. Revenue model to hit $500k profit: - Premium tier: $997-1997/month (100 clients = $100k-200k/month) - Mid tier: $497/month (500 clients = $248k/month) - Entry tier: $97/month (1000 clients = $97k/month) Or focus on high-ticket: - $5k-10k one-time setup + $497-997/month maintenance - Need only 50-100 clients to hit target Let me create detailed tactical SOPs with data tables. View Using Tool | MCP Chart Server MCP: generate_mind_map {\"data\":{\"name\":\"Online Profit Class AI Business Operating System\",\"children\":[{\"name\":\"Core Offer Structure\",\"children\":[{\"name\":\"Premium Tier: $1997/mo\",\"children\":[{\"name\":\"Full AI Agent Suite\"},{\"name\":\"Done-For-You Setup\"},{\"name\":\"Weekly Strategy Calls\"}]},{\"name\":\"Growth Tier: $497/mo\",\"children\":[{\"name\":\"Core AI Agents\"},{\"name\":\"Template Library\"},{\"name\":\"Group Support\"}]},{\"name\":\"Starter Tier: $97/mo\",\"children\":[{\"name\":\"Content AI Tools\"},{\"name\":\"Basic Automation\"},{\"name\":\"Community Access\"}]}]},{\"name\":\"AI Agent Capabilities\",\"children\":[{\"name\":\"Content Creation Suite\",\"children\":[{\"name\":\"Viral Hook Generator\"},{\"name\":\"Reel Script Writer\"},{\"name\":\"Email Sequence Builder\"},{\"name\":\"Sales Copy Creator\"}]},{\"name\":\"Marketing Automation\",\"children\":[{\"name\":\"Instagram DM Bot\"},{\"name\":\"Email Nurture Flows\"},{\"name\":\"Ad Creative Generator\"},{\"name\":\"Landing Page Builder\"}]},{\"name\":\"Audience Growth\",\"children\":[{\"name\":\"Viral Content Strategy\"},{\"name\":\"Engagement Optimizer\"},{\"name\":\"Lead Magnet Creator\"},{\"name\":\"Comment Automation\"}]}]},{\"name\":\"Traffic Sources\",\"children\":[{\"name\":\"Organic Instagram\",\"children\":[{\"name\":\"2x Daily Posting\"},{\"name\":\"Comment Automat